/// Render a band-table report for this probe. `as_ticks`
/// controls the display unit: `false` converts stored tick
/// deltas to nanoseconds (default for the CLI); `true` shows
/// raw ticks (`-t`/`--ticks`). `overhead` (if `Some`)
